flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{Decision}
    B -->|yes| C[Do work]
    C --> D{More?}
    D -->|yes| B
    D -->|no| E[Done]

    subgraph Iteration Loop
        E --> F[Step]
        F --> G{Issue?}
        G -- yes --> H[Review]
        H --> I[Plan]
        I --> J[Edit]
        J --> F
        G -- no --> K[Module done]
    end

    K --> L[Module complete]
    L --> M[QA review]
    M --> N{Need refine?}
    N -- yes --> O[Refactor]
    O --> L
    N -- no --> P[Next]
    P --> A
